const char* const AosOpenBottomTraits_2___class__ = "A model of the concept AosOpenBottomTraits_2 must be used when the parameter space of the surface, the arrangement is embedded on, is open on the bottom side and curves inserted into the arrangement are expected to reach this boundary side. A model of this concept can handle curves that reach the bottom boundary side when it is open. Refines AosBottomSideTraits_2 AosOpenLeftTraits_2 , AosOpenRightTraits_2 , AosOpenTopTraits_2 , AosClosedBottomTraits_2 , AosContractedBottomTraits_2 , and AosIdentifiedHorizontalTraits_2";
